---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Stories - RailDevHub" description="Read the inspiring stories behind our railway transformation projects">
  <Header />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 via-white to-blue-50">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold text-railway-steel mb-6">
          Our Stories
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          The journeys behind Turkey's railway digital transformation - from vision to reality
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- RayNext Story -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-12">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">
            Digital Transformation Story
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-railway-steel mb-6">
            RayNext: The Future of Digital Railway
          </h2>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-6 text-gray-600 mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
              Ankara to Istanbul
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
              November 2025
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8">
            <p class="text-xl italic leading-relaxed">
              "A journey that begins from the heart of Turkey, Ankara... A vision crossing Istanbul's bridges... The story of a digital transformation rising above thousands of kilometers of railway networks."
            </p>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-railway-steel mt-8 mb-4">Why RayNext?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            In the modern world of technology, a name must represent both the past and point to the future. <strong>RayNext</strong> strikes exactly this balance:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Ray (Rail):</strong> The soul of railways, the history flowing over steel rails for centuries, respect for Turkey's railway culture</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Next:</strong> Vision for the future, continuous progress, the next phase of digital transformation</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-railway-steel mb-4">The Vision Starting from Ankara</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              In the capital Ankara, a team gathered at the UHDGM (General Directorate of Transportation Services Regulation) building and decided to digitalize the railway sector. Not just software, but a complete ecosystem would be built.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              From type approval processes to vehicle registration; from ECM management to safety certificates; from training centers to train driver management... Everything would be digitalized.
            </p>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-railway-steel mt-8 mb-4">Inspiration from Istanbul</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Istanbul, the city that connects two continents. With its thousands of years of history, this city that blends modern technology inspired our project. Just like the bridge between two continents, <strong>RayNext</strong>, built by <strong>PiA Group</strong>, constructs the bridge between traditional and digital.
          </p>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-primary-100 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-railway-steel mb-3">What RayNext Means</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Gateway to the Future</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Continuous Progress</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ User Experience Excellence</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ National Technology Pride</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ International Standards</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-primary-100 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-railway-steel mb-3">Who Uses RayNext</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li>‚Ä¢ UHDGM Personnel in Ankara</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Applicants Nationwide</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ ECM Organizations</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Training Centers</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Data Analysts</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-railway-steel to-railway-track rounded-2xl p-8 text-white my-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Journey Ahead</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
              <div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">2025</div>
                <p class="text-gray-200">MVP ready for use</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">2026</div>
                <p class="text-gray-200">User feedback improvements</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">2027+</div>
                <p class="text-gray-200">AI integrations & automation</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center my-12">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-railway-steel italic">
              "RayNext: The Future of Railway Starts Today."
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">
              A story that starts from Ankara, draws inspiration from Istanbul, and spreads across Turkey
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-8">
          <a href="/projects" class="btn-primary">
            View RayNext Project Details
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="border-t-2 border-gray-100"></div>

  <!-- RayData Story -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-12">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-railway-signal/10 text-railway-signal rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">
            Data Analytics Story
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-railway-steel mb-6">
            RayData: The Power of Railway Data
          </h2>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-6 text-gray-600 mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
              Istanbul to Ankara
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
              November 2025
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-railway-signal to-red-600 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8">
            <p class="text-xl italic leading-relaxed">
              "A data revolution rising from Istanbul... The story of numbers dancing over the network of thousands of kilometers belonging to Turkey's largest railway operator. Every trip, every ticket, every kilometer... All coming together to shape the future of railway transportation."
            </p>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-railway-steel mt-8 mb-4">Why RayData?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            In the age of data, information is power. <strong>RayData</strong> brings exactly this power to the railway sector:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-railway-signal mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Ray (Rail):</strong> The steel network of railways, thousands of trains, millions of passengers</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-railway-signal mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Data:</strong> The meaning of every trip, every ticket, every kilometer - numbers transforming into decisions</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 mb-8 border-2 border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-railway-steel mb-4">The Vision from Istanbul</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              The heart of Istanbul, one of the technology centers... In this city, as the <strong>PiA Group</strong> team, we are working to contribute to revealing the power of railway data.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              From passenger transportation to freight operations, from fleet maintenance to safety management, from resource planning to real-time tracking... In every area, data would become the center of decision-making processes.
            </p>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-railway-steel mt-8 mb-4">The Need from Ankara</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Ankara, the capital of Turkey. TCDD Transportation's decision center is here. Operations managers, strategy team, financial analysts... All needed better data, faster reports, more in-depth analyses.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            <strong>RayData</strong>, which we developed from Istanbul, empowers decision-makers in Ankara. It enables them to see, understand, and optimize operations thousands of kilometers away in real-time.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-800 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white my-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">RayData's Core Features</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
              <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6">
                <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">3</div>
                <div class="text-gray-200 mb-2">Comprehensive Dashboards</div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Executive, Operations, Analytics</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6">
                <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">100+</div>
                <div class="text-gray-200 mb-2">Detailed Reports</div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Covering all railway operations</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6">
                <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Real-Time</div>
                <div class="text-gray-200 mb-2">Live Monitoring</div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Instant operational insights</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-railway-steel mt-8 mb-4">What RayData Means</h3>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-railway-steel mb-3">üìä Data Democratization</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Users at every level can access the data they need</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-railway-steel mb-3">‚ö° Decision-Making Speed</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700">The ability to make quick decisions with instant data</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-railway-steel mb-3">üéØ Operational Excellence</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Data-driven optimization and continuous improvement</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-railway-steel mb-3">üîê Safety Priority</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Risk management and preventive measures with data</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-8 my-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-railway-steel mb-4">Expected Impact</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">15%</div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Operational efficiency increase</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">40%</div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Decision-making times shortened</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">&lt;2s</div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Data access time</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">90%+</div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">User satisfaction target</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center my-12">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-railway-steel italic">
              "RayData: The Power of Railway Data, Being Discovered Today."
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">
              A story that starts from Istanbul, reaches Ankara, and adds value across Turkey
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-8">
          <a href="/projects" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-railway-signal text-base font-medium rounded-lg text-railway-signal bg-transparent hover:bg-railway-signal hover:text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-railway-signal transition-all duration-200">
            View RayData Project Details
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-8 py-16 md:px-16 md:py-20 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Want to Know More About Our Projects?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-primary-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Explore detailed technical information and see how we're transforming railway operations
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/projects" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-primary-600 text-lg font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
              View All Projects
            </a>
            <a href="/about" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white text-white text-lg font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-200">
              About Our Team
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
